{"tid":797863,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好唔捨得一個EX","createTime":"2018-08-29T00:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T07:42:27.000Z","uid":204788,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"984e5497968a29af428cabc64694377ddc71fa98","tid":797863,"uid":204788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:34:56.000Z","msg":"幾年前我仲係一隻中學雞嘅時候<br />\n喺IG見到一個好Pure好True嘅女仔<br />\n又俾我有機會同佢認識到<br />\n佢細我兩年 之前又喺我學校附近嘅學校讀過<br />\n慢慢開始日日傾ws 到一齊去掃街 <br />\n<br />\n未一齊嘅時候你都親手餵我食雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係warm到入骨<br />\n我電話壞咗又肯同我用電腦傾電話<br />\n無所不談<br />\n後尾知道你俾兩個ex屌過 我都從冇介意過<br />\n仲記得我哋行行吓街拖住我手臂 到慢慢拖住我隻手<br />\n呢啲片段我都未忘記過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解之好哋哋一齊咗 又要掉低我自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你話你有想專心做嘅事 好 我祝福你<br />\n<br />\n但係點解過多一年幾又同人開始啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每一次睇到你IG Story 都好似俾人插一刀咁 好痛好痛<br />\n<br />\n近排你好似同佢散咗<br />\n<br />\n我應唔應該再次鼓起勇氣搵多你一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f681116de76db817eae5e06c0dded1d7deefc16","tid":797863,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:51:52.000Z","msg":"唔好害鳩人啦"},{"pid":"44c3437055cd950a31fcbf3c31d250dcd8755a29","tid":797863,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T00:57:28.000Z","msg":"咁搵lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但你真係唔介意？"},{"pid":"6e58d3279e2a133b81fd8d1a4bb9593aadb15c17","tid":797863,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T01:04:33.000Z","msg":"擺明飛鳩你啦<br />\n搵乜柒呀"},{"pid":"f6c12a05ab7c067d0579bf2bc4d17c0c8ce3be0d","tid":797863,"uid":60648,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T01:47:56.000Z","msg":"過多一年幾都唔可以拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <im